  <section class="heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 align-middle">
          <div class="heading__subheadline">
            <h2>What is Pueblo Unido?</h2>
            <div class="horizontal-line">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="heading__text heading__text--medium-width">
            <p>Pueblo Unido is a non-profit organization that supports Portland metro community members in the fight against deportation. We connect clients to adequate legal representation and help gather evidence to strengthen cases against
              removal.
            </p>
            <a class="button" href="volunteer.html.en">Volunteer</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12 align-middle">
          <div class="heading__image">
            <iframe width="100%" height="473" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GJVg-gP4H2I" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-7 align-middle">
          <div class="heading__subheadline">
            <h2>Need Help?</h2>
            <div class="horizontal-line">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="heading__text">
            <p>Pueblo Unido provides legal service navigation and client advocate support for immigrants who are currently in removal proceedings. Those who are NOT currently in removal proceedings may contact Pueblo Unido for a list of nonprofit
              organizations
              in the Portland area who may be able to help.
            </p>
            <p>Don’t know whether you’re in removal proceedings or not? </p>
            <a class="button" href="get-help-detention.html.en">Facing Removal</a>
          </div>
          <div class="heading__text heading__text--small-disclaimer">
            <p>*Disclaimer*: Pueblo Unido PDX is not a law firm; we are not attorneys and we do not offer any legal advice. Instead, we help connect clients to experienced immigration attorneys and follow-up to ensure they receive the advice they
              are seeking.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 align-middle">
          <div class="heading__image">
            <img src="./assets/images/pu-images/png/team--july.png" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
