      <div class="horizontal-line"></div>
      <p>Join us for a evening in celebration of the original dreamers - the parents. There will be featured artwork by undocumented artists, special musical guests, a silent auction, as well as food and drinks for all to enjoy! Visit the Una Vida Mejor <a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/254402461937276/">event page</a> for more information.</p>
